Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.46,0:00:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（六個月后）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.22,0:00:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩列火車 兩個不同的篇章\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Two trains, two chapters to tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.06,0:00:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一列高速飛馳\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One runs hot and fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.31,0:00:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一列蹣跚而行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The other lumbers slow...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.44,0:00:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是威爾福德鐵腕掌控下的列車\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cold-cast in Wilford's iron grip...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.57,0:00:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一只在兔子身后策劃陰謀的 武裝的烏龜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}An armored tortoise plodding after a hare...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.32,0:00:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人都受同一個人控制\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everyone under a single thumb...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.62,0:00:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服務于同一個偏執的目標…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Serving a single obsession...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.58,0:00:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奪回被盜的東西 實施他的報復\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To retake the pirates and exact his revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.96,0:00:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能聞到他們的氣味\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can smell them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.46,0:00:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從結冰情況來看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Layton took my engine through here
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.72,0:00:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大約一個月前 雷頓把我的機車帶到這里來過\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}about a month ago, judging by the ice buildup.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.72,0:00:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經緊隨其后了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Practically on their heels.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.97,0:00:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到沒 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You see?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.10,0:01:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像雪地里的足跡一樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Like old footprints in the snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.48,0:01:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工程師 轉到往南去的岔路上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Set switch for the south fork, Engineer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.44,0:01:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會把它奪回來的 朱庇特 不惜任何代價\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll get it back, Jupe, whatever it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.19,0:01:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,列車鳴汽笛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.86,0:01:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,催人眼迷離
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.58,0:01:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男孩女孩們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.12,0:01:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鉆進毯子里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.83,0:01:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司機伴引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.55,0:01:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消防員按鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.13,0:01:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡魔搖燈籠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.72,0:01:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都安寧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.64,0:01:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路搖啊晃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.39,0:01:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沿海灣啟程
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.94,0:01:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跋涉數千里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.69,0:01:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開往晨光鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.28,0:01:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,列車途經處
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.16,0:02:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許在下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.70,0:02:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有小旅客…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.58,0:02:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,列車里是一個倒退的世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Inside, it's a backwards world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.46,0:02:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今只有一個階級了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Only one class now,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.21,0:02:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是工人階級\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the working class, freezing, stitching,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.92,0:02:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,縫補修葺 忍凍受罪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}fixing, suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.22,0:02:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跋涉數千里 開往晨光鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.19,0:02:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 這里不是過道 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hey, this isn't a pass-through.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.83,0:02:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-溫妮佩 -有給頭兒捎的信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Winnipeg. - Message for the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.09,0:02:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 挨凍的人們更會抱作一團\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- But frostbitten fingers hold fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.01,0:03:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在寒冰深處 威爾福德從不涉足的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Deep in the iced-over bowels where Wilford never treads...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.47,0:03:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依然有一絲火花在閃耀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A spark still lives:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.18,0:03:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是抵抗軍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the resistance,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.14,0:03:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由勇者中的勇者培養并守護著\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}nurtured and protected by the bravest of the brave.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.95,0:03:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給頭兒捎的信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Message for the tippity-top.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.57,0:03:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派克先生 你沒說暗號\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I didn't hear the password, Mr. Pike.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.78,0:03:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的二把手 我對你的期望比這要高\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I expect more from my second in command.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.79,0:03:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們發現了雪國列車的蹤跡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They picked up sign of Snowpiercer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.21,0:03:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已轉向南面 回到了主軌道上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We turned south, back on the main line.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.21,0:03:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝天謝地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, thank God for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.75,0:03:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,32天了 這是第一個 證明他們還活著的消息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is the first proof we've had that they are still alive in 32 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.55,0:03:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們這樣到處閑轉 一定有他們的原因\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They must--they must have their reasons for all this traipsing about.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.89,0:03:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果梅蘭妮在列車上的話\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, if Melanie's aboard--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.14,0:03:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這又說不定的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.60,0:03:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯絲 晚上你一個人 待在這下面時 有沒有想過\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You ever think, Ruth, all alone down here at night,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.52,0:03:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然當初是雷頓拋下了我們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that since Layton bailed on us in the first place,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.98,0:03:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可能永遠都不會回來了 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}he might never come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.11,0:03:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想過\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.61,0:04:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也沒有 否則你不會加入抵抗軍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And neither do you, or you wouldn't be in the resistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.99,0:04:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 這些抗生素給裁縫們 她們會需要的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- So antibiotics for the seamstresses. They'll need them,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.54,0:04:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都擠在那個血汗工廠里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}all jammed up together in that sweatshop.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.83,0:04:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些小小的補給品能讓我們保持理智\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's these little things that will keep us sane, Mr. Pike.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.38,0:04:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我們能讓旅途稍微舒服點 乘客們就能熬過這一關\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The passengers can survive all of this if we can ease their journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.51,0:04:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他們為雷頓先生的歸來做好準備\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And keep them ready for Mr. Layton's return.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.72,0:04:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威爾福德1023節車廂長的集中營 轟隆前行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- The heart of hope still beats aboard Wilford's rolling gulag,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.43,0:04:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在車上依然跳動著滿懷希望的心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}1,023 cars long.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.80,0:05:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 這里應該不會有軌道污染物了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay. Should be clear of track contaminants.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.72,0:05:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要開始采集冰樣了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm gonna start pulling ice samples.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.27,0:05:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面看上去怎么樣 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How's it looking?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.52,0:05:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棕櫚樹 金沙灘\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Palm trees, golden sands.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.73,0:05:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得去趕朝鮮的海浪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gotta catch me some North Korean waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.19,0:05:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不錯 我去拿一下沖浪板 馬上就出去 兄弟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Nice. I'll grab my board. I'll be right out, bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.53,0:05:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他集中精力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Let him focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.44,0:05:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我是在幫他保持冷靜 -你是在讓他分心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'm keeping him calm. - You're distracting him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.78,0:05:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本 你的防護服還能堅持22分鐘 你的心率正常\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Ben, the suit's at 22 minutes. Your heart rate's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.20,0:05:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用緊張 好嗎 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You steady on, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.82,0:05:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Copy that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.00,0:05:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引擎運轉得好點了嗎 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Engine any happier?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.80,0:05:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在排放燃料 但還是過熱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We're venting, but still too hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.67,0:05:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面的情況如何 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How's it looking?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.55,0:05:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“零下86攝氏度”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, minus 86.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.80,0:05:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 虧我們還大老遠跑來這里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, well, I'm sure glad we came all this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.22,0:05:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別把天氣和氣候的概念搞混了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Well, don't mistake the weather for the climate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.10,0:05:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本采集的樣本會顯示氣候的全貌\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ben's samples will show us the full picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.64,0:05:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是在尋找趨勢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're looking for trends.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.15,0:05:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為我們是在找宜居的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I thought we were looking for a place to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.36,0:06:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,模型說這里是合適地點 等采樣結果出來再說\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The model likes this spot. Let's just wait for the results.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.78,0:06:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“模型”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, the model.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.19,0:06:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 提爾 還記得之前 模型說蘇拉威西島很合適嗎 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hey, Till, remember how much the model liked Sulawesi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.03,0:06:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.66,0:06:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們環行世界六個月了 卻沒拿得出手的成績\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Six months of going around the world with nothing to show for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.62,0:06:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一次停留 我們都了解到了新信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- And we learned something from every stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.45,0:06:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-就把它們當作是數據點嘛 -行 雷頓教授\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Think of them as data points.  Okay, Professor Layton.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.00,0:06:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些不是冰凍的地獄 而是數據點\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- They were not frozen hellscapes. They were data points.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.92,0:06:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.43,0:06:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.43,0:06:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（熱敏開關故障）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.89,0:06:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我需要跟他通話 -好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I need to talk to him. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.60,0:06:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本 主管道上的一個熱敏開關壞了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Ben, we just blew a thermal switch on the main line.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.73,0:06:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-準是誤報 -不是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- It's gotta be an error. - It isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.11,0:06:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你說過 我們的空燃比太小了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We came in too rich. I told you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.94,0:06:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把多余的燃料排出去就行 艾莉 引擎自己會調整的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Just discharge the excess, Alex. She'll rebalance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.45,0:06:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若再繼續排放燃料 我們就會啟動不了了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If I discharge any more, we won't be able to get going again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.82,0:06:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們必須放棄行動 讓他回來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have to abort. Pull him in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.41,0:06:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別聽她的 雷頓 她能調整好空燃比的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's wrong, Layton. She can ride the levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.41,0:06:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再給我十分鐘\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ten more minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.54,0:06:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在大量耗費燃料 我們得馬上啟程\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We're burning up. We need to go right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.50,0:07:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡你所能穩住引擎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do what you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.75,0:07:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟他說了空燃比太小\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I told him we came in too rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.71,0:07:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.18,0:07:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切盡在掌握之中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everything's under control.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.09,0:07:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本 你繼續完成任務 好嗎 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Ben, just stay on task. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.20,0:07:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.33,0:07:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她今天早上發過脾氣嗎 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She touchy this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.74,0:07:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常尖酸刻薄\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Scathing. So mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.75,0:07:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-賽克斯馬上就到 -很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Sykes is on her way. - Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.42,0:07:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們為什么又停下了 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why have we stopped again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.96,0:07:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們找不到綠洲的 這你很清楚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, they're not gonna find an oasis. - You know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.13,0:07:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都不清楚 這樣更容易些\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I don't know anything. It's easier that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.30,0:07:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟誰都不熟 什么感覺都沒有 我的囚犯 你是個孤獨的女人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Ugh, know no one, feel nothing. You're a woman alone, my jailer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.93,0:07:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少我還有你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, at least I got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.72,0:07:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想規規矩矩地在外面吃呢 還是想在里面吃 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You gonna be civil, or do you want me to feed you in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.31,0:08:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禽獸優先\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Monsters first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.39,0:08:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-不 請吧 -不要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No, please. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.77,0:08:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 能選的越來越少 這是今天的選擇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Okay. Today's dwindling selection.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.82,0:08:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們有紅酒燉牛肉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have the boeuf bourguignon,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.40,0:08:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,培根蛋醬意面、可怕的蘑菇雞肉套餐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the carbonara, the dreaded chicken mushroom bag,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.66,0:08:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有最后一份泰式蔬菜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and the last Thai vegetable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.03,0:08:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給這些鐵路強盜干活 你好像挺開心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You seem to enjoy working for these pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.54,0:08:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧德麗 我只是個服刑中的戰俘而已\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Just a POW doing my time, Audrey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.12,0:08:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這么配合他們 他會惡心死的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Well, he'd be disgusted with your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.46,0:08:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能別拌嘴了嗎 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can you please?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.17,0:08:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-如果沒人想要泰式蔬菜… -馬汀 給我培根蛋醬意面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- If nobody wants the Thai vegetable... - Just give me the carbonara, Martin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.67,0:08:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,培根蛋醬意面是最難吃的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Carbonara, it's the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.93,0:08:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本 風開始大了 看來有冷鋒要來了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Ben? Ben, the wind's picking up. It looks like there's a front coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.64,0:08:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到 我這就回去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Copy that. I'm on my way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.93,0:08:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉那里情況如何 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- How's Alex?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.85,0:08:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉 匯報情況\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Alex, status.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.85,0:08:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引擎沒有著火\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're not actively on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.35,0:08:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他動作快一點\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell him to hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.81,0:08:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說她聽了你的建議 一切運作正常\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- She says she took your advice and everything's working out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.49,0:08:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里有很多飄雪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So much blown snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.28,0:08:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有大量的風吹過這片盆地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A lot of wind comes through this basin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.16,0:08:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是好事 對嗎 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Well, that's good, though, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.12,0:08:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.12,0:08:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是模型測到的暖點引起的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Might be our warm spot stirring things up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.93,0:09:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（信號丟失）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.60,0:09:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-本  -本 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Ben. - Ben?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.81,0:09:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-本  -本 收到請回答 本\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Ben. - Ben, come in, Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.81,0:09:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我看不到他了 -本 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I can't see him. - Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.40,0:09:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本 聽到我說話了沒 本 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Ben! Ben, do you copy? Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.11,0:09:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本 聽到沒有 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ben, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.05,0:09:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝絲 有件事我不明白\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The bit I don't get, Bess,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.13,0:09:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等把你們那寶貝氣候模型 帶回給威爾福德之后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when we return to Wilford with your precious climate model,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.59,0:09:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們打算怎樣 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}what happens then?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.18,0:09:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,談判\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Negotiations.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.01,0:10:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩列列車都想重新連接\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Both trains want to reconnect.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.47,0:10:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 先談交換人質的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yeah. Hostage negotiations first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.68,0:10:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你換扎拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You for Zarah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.27,0:10:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行 然后呢 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yeah, but then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.02,0:10:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你們這里的七個人 換威爾福德手里的2700個 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Wilford's 2,700 to your 7?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.48,0:10:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對叛徒和偷渡者 他可不會客氣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's not gonna take too kindly to a traitor and a stowaway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.24,0:10:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么成偷渡者了 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How am I a stowaway?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.28,0:10:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當時在自己的車廂里打盹 醒來時列車已經不見了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I woke up from a nap in my carriage and the train was gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.20,0:10:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連同我的老公和雙胞胎兒子一起沒了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}along with my husband and my twin boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.66,0:10:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是提爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Till here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.58,0:10:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得把他們關起來 然后到上面來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yeah, I need you to lock them down and get up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.45,0:10:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-出什么事了  -沒什么是他們需要知道的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What's up? - Nothing they need to know about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.79,0:10:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我這就去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- All right. On my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.21,0:10:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本 聽到沒有 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ben, do you read?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.04,0:10:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 午飯結束 馬汀 把她關起來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right, that's lunch. Martin, lock her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.54,0:10:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-出什么事了嗎  -動起來 快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Is something wrong? - Move, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.05,0:10:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 我之前看到本出去了 你們需要幫忙嗎 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hey, I saw Ben going outside earlier. - Do you need help?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.55,0:10:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用 一切都好 我們沒事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No, everything's good. We're good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.10,0:10:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}On it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.56,0:10:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提爾 嘿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Till. Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.56,0:10:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事了 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.60,0:10:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們待在自己的房間里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You stay in your quarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.65,0:10:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著機車給出故障排除的指示\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wait till the engine gives the all-clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.15,0:10:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-就這樣  -是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- That's it? - Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.08,0:11:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我要出去看看 -你不能去 我去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm going out there. - No, you're not. I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.37,0:11:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆都不能出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Neither of you are going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.29,0:11:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不能待在這里 本 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can't stay here. Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.54,0:11:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-本 聽到了沒  -我們不能撇下他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ben, do you copy? We are not leaving him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.96,0:11:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷頓 如果現在不啟動 引擎會燒壞的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Layton, if we don't get rolling right now, we will melt down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.59,0:11:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你需要多少時間 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How long do you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.51,0:11:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八分鐘啟動加速\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- 8 minutes to get up to speed,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.09,0:11:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10到12分鐘運行燃料釋放程序\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}10 to 12 minutes to run a discharge sequence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.39,0:11:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-很好 開始吧 -把你丟在外面嗎 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Great. Go. - And leave you outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.39,0:11:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搶修員的防護服能維持30分鐘 你啟動列車 然后再回來找我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- The breach suits have 30 minutes. You go, you come back for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.39,0:11:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你得留下 -聽你的才怪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You are staying here. - Yeah. Like, hell I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.11,0:11:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什么可討論的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not a discussion, Josie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.19,0:11:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我們三個都出了事 就沒人能完成戶外任務了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If all three of us get in trouble out there, there's no one left for off-train work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.40,0:11:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會確保這情況不會發生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yeah, well, I'll make sure that doesn't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.57,0:11:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這么一次\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You know, one time,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.99,0:11:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩你改變一下習慣 服從指揮吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}just for a change of pace, you could respect the chain of command.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.08,0:11:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“服從指揮” \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Chain of command?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.04,0:11:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷頓 這不是艘戰艦 而是個救生筏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Layton, this isn't a battleship. It's a bloody life raft.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.13,0:11:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得留在筏上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you're staying on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.88,0:11:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本根本就不該出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Ben shouldn't even be out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.55,0:12:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-他知道自己在做什么 -是呀 追逐梅蘭妮的鬼魂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- He knew what he was getting into. - Yeah. Chasing Melanie's ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.64,0:12:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是驗證她的理論\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Her theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.47,0:12:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們都說好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We all agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.93,0:12:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到新伊甸園 再回去接大伙兒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We find New Eden, then we go back for the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.77,0:12:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬一沒有新伊甸園呢 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- And what if there is no New Eden?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.31,0:12:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬一她錯了呢 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What if she's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.48,0:12:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就跟她一起完蛋 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Guess we just all go down with her, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.86,0:12:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提爾 你得負責駕駛 把我們帶出這里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Till, you're gonna have to pilot us out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.95,0:12:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 為什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Me? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.41,0:12:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我得處理這個\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Because I need to go deal with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.12,0:12:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.87,0:12:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, Jesus. Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.04,0:12:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行 好 交給我了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, okay. I--I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.13,0:12:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（勿碰）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.59,0:12:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（危險）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.85,0:12:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那些天花亂墜的話 連自己都開始信了 你知道的吧 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You're starting to believe your own hype. You do know that, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.85,0:12:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是在努力讓大家都活下去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'm just trying to keep everyone alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.98,0:12:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 我們知道 你是我們偉大的救世主\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yep. We know. Our great savior.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.06,0:12:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從沒這么說過\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Never my words.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.56,0:12:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從一開始就在末等車廂 臟的臭的我都經歷過\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I was there at the beginning in The Tail, in the muck and the shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.65,0:12:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你的為人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.28,0:13:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當初是你鼓勵我當領袖的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You encouraged me to be a leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.20,0:13:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是領導這個\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Not for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.45,0:13:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這都不是我想要的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Didn't ask for any of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.37,0:13:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機車 我們在艙門口了 打開安全閘\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Engine, we're at the bay door. Release the safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.79,0:13:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh, copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.92,0:13:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艙門安全閘在哪兒 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bay door safety?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.54,0:13:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在系統面板的右上角\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}System panel, top right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.40,0:13:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬西 當心點\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Josie, be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.86,0:13:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.82,0:13:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 你也是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.50,0:14:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到什么了嗎 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You see anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.05,0:14:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們在另一邊 這里看不到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're on the wrong side.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.13,0:14:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經停了很長時間了 不是嗎 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, we've been stopped for an awfully long time, haven't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.31,0:14:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-機車 我們已下車了 -好 收到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Engine, we're clear. - Okay. Copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.77,0:14:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們下車了 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.94,0:14:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能啟動 加速到20嗎 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Okay. Take us up to 20.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.23,0:14:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠著點 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Easy! Easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.72,0:14:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是總的合并分類帳\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- This is the general consolidated ledger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.68,0:14:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從中可以看到 司務長是在哪個環節 發現偷竊行為的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you can see where the quartermaster detected pilfering.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.81,0:15:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧妙地分攤到了供應鏈的各個環節\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Cleverly dispersed along the supply chain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.28,0:15:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是雷頓的余黨干的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Laytonites, or what's left of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.69,0:15:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 有人在扮演羅賓漢呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yeah. Someone's playing Robin Hood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.12,0:15:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎拉 你感覺如何 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Zarah. Zarah. How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.37,0:15:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-非常龐大 我挺好 謝謝關心 -很好…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Enormous. - I'm fine, thank you. Oh, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.17,0:15:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈維 我拿到了工程部的報告\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I have the engineering report, Javi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.46,0:15:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-給我吧 -我們來聽她說吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'll take that. - Let's hear it from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.51,0:15:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎拉 我很欣賞你傳遞壞消息的方式\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I appreciate how you deliver bad news, Zarah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.67,0:15:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你總能保持心明眼亮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Always a clear-eyed view.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.14,0:15:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- So, then,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.97,0:15:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大部分二等車廂 和部分三等車廂的水管還凍著\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}your water pipes are still frozen. Most of Second and parts of Third.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.89,0:15:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,農業區的產量又下降了 不過本周只下降了6%\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And Ag-Sec output is down again, but only by 6% this week.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.44,0:15:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是因為有人盜竊…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- This is pilfering. I was--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.40,0:15:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚 43個休眠者 以及串連區的供熱完全斷了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- And last night, 43 sleepers and The Chains lost heat completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.99,0:15:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍有162名乘客處于疏散狀態\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}162 passengers remain evacuated.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.65,0:15:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我們沒法同時為所有人供暖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Well, if we can't keep them all warm at once,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.70,0:15:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那他們就得分批挨凍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}they'll just have to be miserable in shifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.08,0:15:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拋棄頭等車廂呀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll cut First Class.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.41,0:15:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Out of the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.50,0:16:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約瑟夫 你已經將其棄置 都空了 又結了冰 拋棄它可以減輕負擔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Well, you did decommission it, Joseph. It's empty and frozen. - Cut the weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.12,0:16:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我把機車和奧德麗奪回來之后 就會讓頭等車廂重現輝煌\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I will restore First to glory when I get my engine back-- and Audrey with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.42,0:16:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許有其他節約能源的方法 比如選擇性宰殺\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Perhaps there's another way to conserve energy. - Like a cull.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.80,0:16:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 凱文 你這個食人魔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No, Kevin, you ghoul.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.26,0:16:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請教訓一下他 提醒他這里是有規矩的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Please berate him. Remind him there are rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.39,0:16:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉得讓你失望了 凱文\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sorry to disappoint, Kevin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.80,0:16:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了凍斷一兩根手臂 我們要盡可能保證大家活著\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But minus an arm or two, we keep everyone as alive as possible
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.14,0:16:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣 奧德麗才能活著\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so Audrey stays as alive as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.06,0:16:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-明白 -你也一樣 親愛的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Of course. - And you too, my dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.98,0:16:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是答應了的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- That's been guaranteed,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.53,0:16:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是嗎 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.74,0:16:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見 哈維\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bye, Javi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.70,0:16:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,規矩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.54,0:16:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抵抗軍可沒這么規矩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The resistance is not so constrained.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.91,0:16:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱文 所有游戲都有規矩 有點創意嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Every game has rules, Kevin. Get creative.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.50,0:17:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍靴泰森\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jackboot Tyson.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.87,0:17:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底能不能把我調出堆肥區 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Can you get me out of compost or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.71,0:17:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再等一周\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One more week.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.04,0:17:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 趁等的時候 洗個熱水盆浴怎么樣 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But in the meantime, how about a nice hot bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.51,0:17:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是在取笑我嗎 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You taking the piss?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.26,0:17:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沐浴券 獎勵你為抵抗事業作出的貢獻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bathing token for services to the cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.06,0:17:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱文 要喝點什么嗎 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What can we do for you, Kevin?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.23,0:17:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我來杯阿華田\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ovaltine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.32,0:17:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這里沒有阿華田 只有列車自釀的烈酒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, we don't have Ovaltine. We have train-made hooch.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.36,0:17:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 來一杯那個酒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Fine. One hooch.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.57,0:17:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威爾福德先生很喜歡 你們打理這里的方式\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. Wilford loves what you've done with the place,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.12,0:18:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 他需要你們多做一件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I'm afraid he needs just a smidge more from the deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.75,0:18:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打聽消息 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Information?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.46,0:18:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抵抗軍在不停地 各處討好 盜取資源\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- The subversives continue filching and currying favor
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.97,0:18:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而他們的首領 則不斷從我們指縫里溜走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}while their shot caller keeps slipping through our fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.18,0:18:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在希望能找出并抓住這個人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We would like this person identified and captured... now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.23,0:18:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許喝醉的那個軍靴知道點內幕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Maybe our passed-out Jack knows something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.98,0:18:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍靴惠金斯 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jackboot Whiggins?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.11,0:18:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 斯圖 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oi, Stuie.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.57,0:18:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-惠金斯 醒一醒 -干嗎 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wake up, Whiggins. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.24,0:18:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說我可以待在這里的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You said I could stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.45,0:18:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你是負責看守水資源的吧  -嗯 怎么了 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- They put you on Water Security, yeah? Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.66,0:18:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以前是頭等車廂的 所以你會樂意幫忙的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You're a former Firstie, so you'll be glad to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.62,0:18:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水資源的安全出了什么問題 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Well, what's happening in Water Security?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.54,0:18:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有問題啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh, you know, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.42,0:18:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.84,0:18:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Um, well,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.09,0:18:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是很小的問題\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you know, very little.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.31,0:19:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-凱文需要的不多 -只需要一點線索就行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Kevin doesn't need much. - Just a little thread to pick.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.68,0:19:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.98,0:19:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 我聽說二等車廂的配水員\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Well, I've heard that the Second Class Watermaster
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.56,0:19:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在給為抵抗軍效力的人…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}was giving away hot baths
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.44,0:19:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提供免費熱水盆浴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for service to the resistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.36,0:19:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們來看看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's have a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.91,0:19:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷口恢復得很不錯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, that's healing nicely.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.54,0:19:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天涂藥膏了嗎 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have you applied your cream today?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.75,0:19:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-沒有 先生 -那就讓我來幫你涂吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No, sir. - Well, then allow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.22,0:19:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 乖狗狗 沒事的 躺下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, it's all right, cub. It's all right. You like me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.89,0:19:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱庇特的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This business with Jupiter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.14,0:19:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈維爾 我知道 用它對付人的手法很粗暴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know she's a blunt tool, Javier.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.44,0:19:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 當你一個人 得為近三千人負責時\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But when you're one man responsible for nearly 3,000...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.86,0:19:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是紀律嚴明是不夠的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not enough being a disciplinarian.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.20,0:20:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得再用上別的手段才行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You need to add a little chaos to the mix.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.41,0:20:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這里 就是朱庇特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In here, it's Jupiter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.99,0:20:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在外面 就是凱文 咬牙切齒 橫沖直撞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Out there, it's Kevin, gnashing his teeth and running amok.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.00,0:20:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈維爾 你無法與不可預測的事情作對\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can't fight the unpredictable, Javier.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.83,0:20:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我確保大家安全的方法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's how I keep everyone safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.13,0:20:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.26,0:20:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你能看清問題的本質\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I hope you see it for what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.59,0:20:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我確實很需要你 哈維爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I do need you, Javier.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.85,0:20:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好小伙子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.78,0:20:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是威爾福德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wilford.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.03,0:20:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先生 我們有線索了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sir, we have a lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.13,0:21:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,配水員阿諾多雷耶斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Watermaster Arnoldo Reyas.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.47,0:21:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永恒機車永不停歇\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Sí, señor. The Engine will provide.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.98,0:21:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清新如洗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Clean as a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.20,0:21:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.33,0:21:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出來吧 別著涼了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on out before you get cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.59,0:21:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,配水員把我們的位置告訴了他們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- The Watermaster told them where we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.26,0:21:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-得換地方了 -又要換 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Gotta go. - Again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.98,0:21:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-好了嗎  -好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Okay. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.10,0:21:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-來吧 -來了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Come on. - I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.39,0:21:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就對了 就是這樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- There you go, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.31,0:22:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我們走吧 快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Oh. - No, no, no, no, no, no. Ruth, let's go, quick. Quick, quick, quick, quick, quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.15,0:22:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- All right. All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.03,0:22:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是所有人都像你行動這么迅速\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can't all be built like a bloody whippet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.12,0:22:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.21,0:22:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們得走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We gotta go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.76,0:22:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Let's go. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.21,0:23:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終點站到了 當然 這里都結冰了 通勤車不能通行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}End of the line. The First is too frozen for the subtrain.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.09,0:23:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.26,0:23:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊 這里真冷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Crikey, it's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.43,0:23:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 等一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.40,0:23:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們在這里待過 就在我們的眼皮底下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- They were here. Right under our noses.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.66,0:23:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背信棄義\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Treachery.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.87,0:23:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你個機靈鬼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Who are you,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.20,0:23:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you clever thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.16,0:23:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們把這里的供熱調得很低 一直都在零下25度\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- They got it on trickle, stays around minus 25.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.25,0:23:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望他們不會找到這里來 因為這里太冷 沒法生活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm hoping they won't look back here, because, you know, it's too cold to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.18,0:23:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.98,0:24:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 凱文就不能把這里收拾一下 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What, Kevin couldn't put anything away?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.57,0:24:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯絲 在這里面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In here, Ruth.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.74,0:24:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當心頭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Watch your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.12,0:24:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找了幾個同志替你布置了一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Had a couple of our comrades gussy it up for ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.42,0:24:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 零下12度\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}See, minus 12.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.26,0:24:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不錯 謝謝你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- It's lovely, thank you. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.42,0:24:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替我轉達一下謝意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Send my regards down the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.68,0:24:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.76,0:24:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡我這機靈的身板嗎 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What, you likey that I'm built like a whippet?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.47,0:24:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么呀 放尊重點\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No. Mind your cheek.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.69,0:24:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-謝謝你 -不客氣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Thank you. - You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.65,0:24:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷頓先生 如果你在外面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- If you're out there, Mr. Layton,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.66,0:24:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是回來的好時機\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}now would be a great time to come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.48,0:25:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪國列車 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Snowpiercer,"
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.44,0:25:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪國列車 收到請回答\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}come in. "Snowpiercer."
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.49,0:25:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.58,0:25:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（溫度：14度 剩余8分鐘）
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.08,0:25:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 伙計\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.21,0:25:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你帶上沖浪板了嗎 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You bring your surfboard?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.04,0:25:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想著還是改滑雪橇的好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Thought we'd do some sledding instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.13,0:25:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄弟 你的防護服還能撐多久 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, what's your suit at, man?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.09,0:25:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7分45秒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- 7:45.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.84,0:25:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機車怎么樣了 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.93,0:25:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別為機車操心 艾莉在處理呢 本 你有哪里疼嗎 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Don't worry about the Engine. Alex is on it. Where are you hurting, Ben?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.31,0:26:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸口有點疼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bit of pain in the chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.81,0:26:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手指和腳趾能動嗎 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Can you move your fingers and toes?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.85,0:26:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.02,0:26:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我這就下去 -太危險了 雷頓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm coming down. - Too risky, Layton.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.52,0:26:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放根繩子下來…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Send down a rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.23,0:26:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別操心了 你等著 我馬上回來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Oh, man. Don't worry about it. You sit tight, man. I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.70,0:26:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們在排放燃料 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're venting?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.74,0:26:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們只是在緩緩前進 給引擎降溫 我不明白為什么要這樣做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're just rolling fast enough to cool down. - I don't--I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.87,0:26:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我明白 -我覺得他們沒回來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I do. - I don't think they got back on.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.87,0:26:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你在說什么呢  -都有誰在外面 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you talking about? - So who's outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.79,0:26:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道 你覺得他們有事會告訴我嗎 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I don't know. You think they tell me anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.21,0:26:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道本之前下車了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know Ben went out.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.09,0:26:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從我房間的窗口 看到另有兩個人下去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yeah, well, I think I saw two more from my window.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.17,0:26:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那準是艾莉在駕駛列車 她拋棄他們了嗎 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Well, then Alex has to be driving. Did she ditch them?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.59,0:26:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-他們沒接電話 -馬汀 是時候了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're not answering. Martin, it's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.14,0:26:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行 好 那提爾怎么辦 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. Okay. What about Till?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.10,0:26:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只能先去機車 看情況再說\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Well, we'll just have to go to the Engine and find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.02,0:26:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎么回事 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.02,0:26:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們得回去跟另一列列車匯合\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have to get back with the other train.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.78,0:26:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你幫忙 我就不告訴威爾福德 你很配合他們的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Help us, and I won't tell Wilford you've been cooperating.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.57,0:27:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是認真的吧 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you serious right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.08,0:27:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對認真\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Deadly serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.16,0:27:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們必須重新連接 好嗎  我們這都是在干什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, we need to reconnect. Okay? What are we doing out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.17,0:27:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在漫無目的地瞎轉悠 我們快沒食物了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yeah, we've been running around aimlessly. We're running out of food.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.75,0:27:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后一次機會\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Last chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.42,0:27:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要么回到威爾福德身邊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get back with Wilford
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.13,0:27:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要么就給雷頓陪葬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or dig a grave with Layton.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.47,0:27:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就進牢房去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then get in the cage.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.16,0:27:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的時速是多少 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's our speed?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.37,0:27:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-75公里 -好 我們交換一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Um, 75. - Okay, let's switch places;
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.12,0:27:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我起動冷卻程序時 你得待在這里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need you over here while I start the cooling sequence.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.42,0:27:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得給這些電線配對\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, you're gonna match these lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.09,0:27:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍色接藍色 紅色接紅色 諸如此類 明白了嗎 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Blue to blue, red to red, and so on, you got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.17,0:27:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.13,0:27:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制動員 你得確定哦 這些線是帶電的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Be sure, Brakeman, okay? - These currents are live.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.43,0:28:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確定 對顏色嘛 我能行 換吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yeah, match the colors. I got it. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.72,0:28:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 我不是該死的制動員\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I'm not a freaking Brakeman.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.94,0:28:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.02,0:28:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.44,0:28:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬一他們問起來 就說是你逼我放你出來的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, well, just in case they ask, you forced me to let you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.68,0:28:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.99,0:29:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伙計 還剩多少時間 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hey. Time?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.54,0:29:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2分鐘\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Two minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.83,0:29:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 別擔心 兄弟 有足夠的時間\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- All right, not to worry, brother. There's plenty to go around.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.79,0:29:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不多了 雷頓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not too much, Layton.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.13,0:29:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別弄得咱倆都沒時間了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's not both run out.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.88,0:29:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.39,0:29:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 你之前說沖浪的事 你真的沖過浪 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, hey. All that surf stuff you talking, you really do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.10,0:29:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本奈特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bennet.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.23,0:29:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-沖浪的事  -對\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Surfing? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.77,0:29:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我16歲時 在索佩拉納待過一個夏天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, I spent a summer in Sopelana when I was 16.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.66,0:29:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當地人會沖一種叫“馬路牙子”的浪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, the locals surfed a wave called El Bordillo.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.16,0:29:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-是嗎  -是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Oh, yeah? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.04,0:29:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在那浪尖上學到的 比大學七年學的都多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I learned more on that wave than in seven years of university.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.25,0:29:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你后來回去過嗎 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You ever go back?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.75,0:30:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 回去過一次\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, once.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.84,0:30:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-再去的時候 海平面已上升… -好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}By then, the rising sea levels
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.14,0:30:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…改變了海岸線\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}changed the coastline.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.64,0:30:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海浪沒有了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The wave was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.14,0:30:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們該往回開了吧 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Shouldn't we start going back?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.40,0:30:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空燃比還是太低\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're still too rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.57,0:30:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-那要等多久  -我不知道 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Well, how long? - I don't--I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.23,0:30:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 艾莉 你能處理好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hey, hey, hey, hey, Alex, you can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.28,0:30:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-好嗎  -我不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Okay? - I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.08,0:30:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果換作梅蘭妮 她會怎么做 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What would Melanie do?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.08,0:30:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她會直接知道答案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- She would just know the answer. That's what she would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.62,0:30:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 那…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, fine, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.08,0:30:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果換了是本呢 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What would--What would Ben do?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.67,0:30:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他會拿上紙和筆 邊畫邊解釋給你聽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- He would grab a pen and paper and start mansplaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.55,0:30:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 很好 那就大聲把問題列出來吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Okay, good. Just--just talk it out, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.89,0:30:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當初設計這引擎 是為了在負載下高速行駛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Built to work at speed, under load,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.89,0:30:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我們既沒負載也沒速度\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but we have neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.77,0:30:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它成了被困在玩具車上的噴氣發動機\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're a jet engine strapped to a toy wagon.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.02,0:31:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只需急剎車兩次\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All we have to do is stop on a dime
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.86,0:31:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確保不拋錨 也不耗盡燃料 其中一次反向即可\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}without stalling or burning up twice and once in reverse.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.28,0:31:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提爾 我們有三分鐘的時間 可以倒回去接他們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right, Till, there's a three-minute window to reverse back to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.24,0:31:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直在躲著我嗎 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have you been avoiding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.95,0:31:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讓他們把你關在冷藏室里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I told them to lock you in the meat locker.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.96,0:31:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們覺得關在圖書館更安全 如今看來 安全個屁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They thought the library was more secure. So much for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.54,0:31:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們都在外面嗎 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are they all outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.63,0:31:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧德麗 我現在有點忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'm a bit busy right now, Audrey.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.42,0:31:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能看得出來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I can see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.30,0:31:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看呀 看看我有什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look. Look. Look, what I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.22,0:31:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.18,0:31:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們抓我當人質時 它就在我身上了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I had it on me when they took me hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.35,0:31:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等了六個月 就為了這一刻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have been waiting six months for this moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.03,0:31:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在 讓我們談談 回去找“爹地”的事吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now let's talk about going home to Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.66,0:32:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓緊了 我們到上面見 喬西 開始拉吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hold on tight, buddy. I'll see you up there. - Josie, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.92,0:32:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 本\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right, Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.65,0:33:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.66,0:33:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 本 就差一點了 成了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right. Nearly there, Ben. Nearly there. There, it's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.41,0:33:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你上來了 好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Over the edge, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.50,0:33:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬西 把開關扔給我 把他送回去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Josie, throw me the switch and start back with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.17,0:33:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-不行 你不上來 我們不走 -他快不行了 快走 我會趕上的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No, not till you're out of there. He's fading, Josie. Get going. I'll catch up.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.55,0:33:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你的防護服還能撐多久  -足夠久 別擔心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's your suit at? - Plenty. Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.05,0:33:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我隨后就回去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm right behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.93,0:33:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.78,0:33:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（防護服溫度：11度 剩余時間：7分21秒）
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.74,0:35:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（注意：輻射區 污染區）
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.21,0:35:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人嗎 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.76,0:35:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（防護服溫度：9度 剩余時間：4分39秒）
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.26,0:36:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人嗎 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.30,0:37:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷頓 收到請回答 雷頓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Layton, come in, Layton.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.39,0:37:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷頓 快回答 雷頓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Layton, come in, Layton.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.75,0:37:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（防護服溫度：零下12度 剩余時間：0分0秒）
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.76,0:37:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你媽死了 艾莉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Your mother didn't make it, Alex.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.88,0:37:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面有綠洲的那個想法 也隨她而去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And that idea of an oasis out there died with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.81,0:37:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有隨她而去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, it hasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.31,0:37:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得如果你們發現了什么的話\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Well, I think you would all be getting along much better
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.06,0:37:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個的關系會好很多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if you discovered anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.69,0:37:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本不知道我們發現了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Well, you have no idea what we've discovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.45,0:38:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威爾福德有解決方法 艾莉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Wilford has the answers, Alex.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.83,0:38:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續開 就能解決一切問題\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just keep going, and you solve everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.88,0:38:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續開就是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.61,0:38:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不要 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.20,0:38:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離她遠點\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get away from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.70,0:38:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉 我們得回去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alex, you gotta go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.54,0:38:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往前開 艾莉 回他那里去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Ahead, Alex. Back home to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.96,0:38:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不能把他們丟在外面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We can't leave them out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.17,0:38:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么爛好人 艾莉 別聽她的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Don't listen to her bleeding heart, Alex.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.59,0:39:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學一學約瑟夫 算算存活率\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just do the calculus of survival like Joseph would.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.67,0:39:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了 你們倆都閉嘴 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Stop! Both of you, just stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.55,0:39:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見鬼 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.30,0:39:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只管繼續往前開 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.65,0:39:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alex.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.56,0:39:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-把列車停下 -萬一她是對的怎么辦 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alex, stop the train. What if she was right?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.78,0:39:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-萬一威爾福德是最好的選擇呢  -他不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What if Wilford is the best bet? - He's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.36,0:39:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅蘭妮才是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Melanie is.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.11,0:39:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嗎 我們可以熬過這一關的 艾莉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay? We can get through this, Alex.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.95,0:39:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別選錯了方向\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't tip it the wrong way.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.25,0:39:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嗎 好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.95,0:40:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（防護服溫度 零下38度 充電中）
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.03,0:40:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪國列車 收到請回答 雪國列車\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- "Snowpiercer." Come in, "Snowpiercer."
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.33,0:41:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷頓 你聽到了嗎 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Layton, Layton, can you read me?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.75,0:41:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷頓 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Layton.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.17,0:41:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪國列車 收到請回答\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Snowpiercer," come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.67,0:41:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.80,0:41:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里 他們在那里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There. There they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.68,0:41:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只看到兩個人 只有兩個人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's only two-- there's only two of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.52,0:41:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起來 本 起來
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.99,0:41:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-等一下 我的胸部 -坐在那里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Wait, wait. - Sit there.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.75,0:41:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷頓 收到請回答 雷頓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Layton, come in, Layton.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.96,0:41:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷頓 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Layton,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.92,0:41:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷頓 收到請回答\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}come in, Layton.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.18,0:41:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著 我會回來的 好嗎 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, I'll be back, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.97,0:41:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬西 你在外面待得太久了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Josie, you've been out too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.39,0:42:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能找到他的 我去去就回\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I can find him. I'll be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.56,0:42:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬西 他的防護服五分鐘前就沒電了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Josie, his suit ran out five minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.16,0:42:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷頓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Layton. Layton!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.96,0:42:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.29,0:42:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-他在外面嗎 他在嗎  -是的 他在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's there? - Yes. - He's there? He's there.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.28,0:43:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So what can I get you?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.12,0:43:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會說 我想要的一切我都有了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'd say I've got everything I ever wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.71,0:43:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個女朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.29,0:43:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一間夜總會\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a club,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.67,0:43:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有偉大的威爾福德先生的感激\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and the gratitude of the great Mr. Wilford.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.30,0:43:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.30,0:43:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰不想洗個舒適的熱水澡呢 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Wouldn't we all love a nice warm bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.89,0:43:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這兩個家伙為了抵抗軍 從你們這里竊取了熱水\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}These two stole hot water resources from you for the resistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.98,0:43:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他們要干凈…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because they had to be clean...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.65,0:43:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（道路 真理 我們的生存方式）
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.07,0:43:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…你們就沒澡洗了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You go unwashed.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.11,0:43:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You first.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.17,0:43:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.63,0:43:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是值得的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was worth it.
